[{"conversations": [{"content": "……話說回來真是嚇我一跳耶。", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "願望、監獄……還有人格面具嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "還有那個心之怪盜團也是……", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "怎麼了？如果有什麼不懂的，就都提出來問吧。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那我要問囉？你們『心之怪盜團』究竟是個怎麼樣的組織呢？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "到底你們是以什麼為目的，在當怪盜的？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊……這講下去會很花時間……吾輩等人會到壞人創造出的異世界，前去收下扭曲的內心。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣一來，就能讓壞人悔改，並幫助深受其害的人們。總之，改善世道就是吾輩等人的目的。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對！用法律無法制裁的壞人，就由我們來懲處！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "也就是正義的怪盜團嗎。", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "算是吧，但是在監獄就不是扭曲的內心，而是將被奪走的『願望』取回……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……目的是一樣的。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "看來你們也很習慣戰鬥了呢。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "畢竟不知不覺地也累積了不少經驗嘛！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果對手是陰影，就儘管交給我們。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真是可靠啊……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們雖然對付過很多魔獸與帝國兵，但與陰影對戰的經驗卻是相當貧乏。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就算你們這麼說，戰力也是相當強大啊！對吧，JOKER？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，你們相當強。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER……你是怪盜團的團長嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "果然是你嗎……總覺得一點也不意外。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為能明顯地感受到其他的成員對你都特別重視。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "光用看的就能察覺嗎？真厲害啊……", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，你不也一樣嗎？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？我嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對啊。你是首領對吧？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒有錯啦！這傢伙就是我們的大將！", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "殿下是阿爾貝利亞王國的第七王子，同時也是新阿爾貝利亞的統帥。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "哇……真的是個厲害的人……", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這地方叫做阿爾貝利亞王國嗎？", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對。雖然說現在因為某些原因，處在戰火不斷的分裂狀態就是了。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有許多人民正在受苦，而殿下正是那些人的希望。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "貨真價實的王子，加上戰爭……簡直就是不同的世界……", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這裡就是異世界喔？", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是沒錯啦。但明明我們的年齡沒有差很多，他卻已經統領一個國家了……不覺得很厲害嗎？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，以我們的日常生活是無法想像的。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在你們的世界裡，王子或公主很稀奇嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "也不是說沒有……但有多少人呢？SOPHIE，能幫我查一下嗎？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "抱歉……這裡沒有辦法連上網路，所以無法搜尋……", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊，對耶。對不起！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "網路……？那是什麼東西啊……", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "看來有許多情報須要先交流呢。我也想把監獄的事說清楚。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊。如果接下來要一起進行攻略，那事先知道總是比較好。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們也希望能先了解那些。雖然對你們的世界很感興趣，但現在最想知道的是……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在監獄裡的戰鬥方式是吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我知道了，交給我吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "聽你這麼說真令人安心，麻煩你了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。絕對要把大家的願望都取回。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是啊。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（跨越世界的合作關係嗎……事情變得有趣起來了呢！）", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "願望和監獄……嗯，大致的情況我了解了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然關於願望和監獄的部分，吾輩等人也還有許多地方沒辦法理解清楚……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但這些就是吾輩等人目前擁有的所有情報了。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "再來就是實地訓練了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "實地訓練？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "光只有知識也沒辦法做什麼對吧？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如何在監獄裡和陰影戰鬥，就讓吾輩等人來教你們吧！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那種事情輕輕鬆鬆啦！反正大家一起上就是了對吧？", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "用你的那種做法，馬上就會被包圍起來唷！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "要潛伏在黑影中，華麗地收下祕寶！那樣才稱得上是怪盜啦！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "現在就來教你們怎麼做！來吧，跟吾輩走！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "走吧，尤蒂爾。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好的。各位，我們走吧！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "分組的部分，就這樣吧。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "SOPHIE和克菈兒。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請多指教囉，克菈兒。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好的，請妳多多指教。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "PANTHER和耶魯菲莉絲。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "加油囉，耶魯菲莉絲！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，麻煩妳指導我了，PANTHER。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "吾輩和琉卡。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你可要好好跟上喔，琉卡。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有勞你啦，小貓！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "才不是貓咧！真是的，首先吾輩就先從這部分開始好好教你！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "所以，最後就是我和JOKER了呢。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請多指教了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我才是，要請你多關照了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那麼，各組分別開始進行訓練。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "每一組都要打倒30個以上的陰影，然後再回到這裡！聽好了，請務必要……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "符合怪盜的作風，對吧？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "一點也沒錯，JOKER。好，那麼就開始任務了！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……………………", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "怎麼了，尤蒂爾？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，開始有點擔心事情能不能順利了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………首先，去相信大家吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，說得也是啊……我們也出發吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "呼……結束了……", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "辛苦妳了，耶魯菲莉絲！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，PANTHER也辛苦了。果然用不習慣的作戰方式相當消耗精力呢。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "要在高處確認狀況，還要設計偷襲敵人的時機，這就是怪盜的做法嗎……", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒錯，很巧妙對吧？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "很巧妙這說法確實是不錯，但我身為聖騎士，總是被教導要堂堂正正地作戰，所以對我來說……", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊，我已經不行了……", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "發、發生什麼事了？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "SOPHIE小姐說的話我完全沒有辦法理解……", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "為什麼？發現敵人之後就「唰唰」地解決掉然後再「噗碰」。之後就可以「咻咻──」了。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……就像是這樣。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真、真是不容易呢……殿下和琉卡不知道狀況如何。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "少給我老擺出一副前輩的架子！明明就只是隻貓！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就告訴你吾輩不是貓了！要講幾次才懂啊，你這個兔耳！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這沒救了呢……", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "大家都回來了嗎？所以，是在爭執什麼呢？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不知為何沒辦法契合。大家都各做各的……", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "以我的判斷，就這樣到監獄去會很危險……", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是……是嗎……", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過，大家畢竟認識也還不久，沒辦法好好配合也是沒辦法的事。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果能再讓大家互相有更多認識的話，一定可以……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們在那裡做什麼！？", "speakerName": "影", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嘖，被發現了！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且數量很多。這樣下去不太妙！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……那正好。", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我就讓你們見識一下！就算不像MONA說的那樣偷偷摸摸，也是能好好作戰的啦！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂、喂，太亂來是……！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "別吵啦這隻臭貓！吼呀啊啊啊！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那隻笨兔子！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "警戒度正在上升喔！", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "陰影的數量也在增加！", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "怎麼辦，JOKER！？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們不能把琉卡一個人拋下。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "確實……琉卡是王認識的人，而且也還沒有習慣監獄……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那，該怎麼辦……！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯……好，就兵分兩路吧。一組人負責吸引陰影的注意，另一組去帶著琉卡撤出這裡。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "吾輩和PANTHER、SOPHIE來當誘餌，JOKER帶著大家往城裡去。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我明白了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER！？沒問題嗎……！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒時間煩惱了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就是這樣。……吾輩相信你辦得到的，JOKER。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就讓吾輩來做你們的對手！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂，這是打算要做什麼啊！？", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "準備撤退了，琉卡！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是……！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只有這樣才能讓大家都得救。別浪費大家製造出來的機會。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "警戒度又提升了。……快走吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……嗯、嗯嗯。", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "抱歉……因為自己太急躁就衝動了。全都是我的錯……", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "抱歉，JOKER。現在你的夥伴們……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我現在就去把他們救出來。你能幫助我嗎？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，當然，我會幫你的。但是，該怎麼辦……？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "當然是，以怪盜的作風。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "那種作戰，能順利辦到嗎……！？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只有你自己的話太危險了……！還是用別種策略比較好……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，沒問題的。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（為了夥伴……我能感受到他非比尋常的意志。）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（是他的話一定能辦到。他有種特質讓我這麼相信……）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我知道了。既然你都說到這份上了，那就採用這個作戰吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，謝謝你，尤蒂爾。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "各位也能一起協助我嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那當然。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "很好，我們走吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好好看清楚吧。SHOW TIME！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "各位，都準備好了嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，隨時都可以開始喔！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（JOKER，大家能否順利逃出來就看你的表現了。全都拜託你了……！）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "我想拜託尤蒂爾你們負責誘導敵人。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那樣的話你呢？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我去把大家救出來。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就你一個人到敵人的中心去？那種作戰，能順利辦到嗎……！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只有你自己的話太危險了……！還是用別種策略比較好……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，沒問題的。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我知道了。既然你都說到這份上了，那就採用這個作戰吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "由我們來誘導敵人，讓JOKER潛入敵人的本陣把夥伴都救出來。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER確實身手非常高明。但是，這個作戰本身我還是覺得太過危險了。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……你覺得有辦法成功嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "MONA他們一定也是深信JOKER能把大家都救出來，才會自願去當誘餌的。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "所以一定沒問題。我們也相信JOKER吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……說得也是呢。我們就相信他，盡我們的全力吧。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。好，要上囉……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有入侵者！", "speakerName": "影", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（萬事拜託了，JOKER！）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……………………", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（沒有陰影看守，沒問題。）", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（你們一定要平安無事。MONA、PANTHER、SOPHIE……！）", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦，JOKER！？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真的耶，是JOKER。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "大家……都平安無事嗎。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你來救援了呢。吾輩就相信你會來，JOKER。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "突然陰影們開始騷動，然後就連看守的陰影都跑走了。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "之後，我們就從原先已經注意到的排氣口逃出來了。", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這場騷動，是JOKER引起的嗎？", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯……是我和這世界的夥伴們一起做的。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "果然呢。那麼，吾輩等人也來大鬧一場吧。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，走吧！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "呼、呼……！還沒有結束嗎……！", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "可惡！居然不斷給我冒出來！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "總之要撐下去！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（JOKER，快點……！）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！尤蒂爾！", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（來不及了……）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "讓你們久等了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER！大家……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "心之怪盜團！狀態絕佳地登場啦！！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "要上囉！發動總攻擊！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這就是最後一擊了！上吧！JOKER！尤蒂爾！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們就收下了！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣就結束了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "所以呢，怎麼樣？有稍微在反省了嗎？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，真的是很抱歉……！", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不、不要這麼認真道歉啦！這樣太尷尬了吧！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這就是我對力量過度自信，擅自闖入敵陣的後果。", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為我的關係害大家陷入危機，真的很抱歉……", "speakerName": "琉卡", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不、不是啦，反、反正你別在意了啦！", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個……我也想要道歉，可以嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我……當時還覺得怪盜的做法不對，總覺得有些不光明磊落。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯……", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是我錯了。在監獄裡你們的做法才是正確的。透過這次的事情，我終於明白了。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為和自己的想法不同，所以就起了疑心，真的很抱歉。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "大家都只是還不知道而已。不論是監獄的事，還是彼此的事。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊……我也沒有辦法理解SOPHIE小姐所說的話。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，往後我們一定能互相理解。我有這種感覺。", "speakerName": "克菈兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "從現在起加深彼此的理解就好。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。我們也會努力的。作為協助者，希望能得到你們的信賴。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "說協助者太死板了啦。這時說是『夥伴』就好了嗎？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們願意……當我們是夥伴嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "當然。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "（透過和他的握手，感受到了不僅是單純交易的羈絆……）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "好，已經確保脫離路線沒問題了。物資方面的準備如何？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，傷藥和裝備都已經備齊囉。攻略監獄的準備工作都完成了。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "再來就剩決定什麼時候執行了。要什麼時候出擊呢？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……………………", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "尤蒂爾？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊，抱歉。妳叫我嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我想問你要什麼時候出擊……還好吧？看你好像有點恍神。", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊……可能是有點累了。抱歉，讓妳擔心了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我稍微去休息一下。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "尤蒂爾變得不像是尤蒂爾了。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那傢伙是作戰的關鍵。有點令人擔心啊……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "………………", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "………………", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你在迷惘嗎？", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……JOKER。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是啊，要說我都沒有迷惘，那一定是騙人的。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為埃米爾的事嗎？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。我真的從來沒想過事情會變成這樣。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "所以不禁會覺得，在事情變成這樣之前，我是不是能做些什麼才對……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "到底我有沒有哪裡做錯了……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "………………", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "怎麼了……你就只是看著嗎？為了明哲保身，要見死不救嗎？再這樣下去他就真的要死了喔？", "speakerName": "亞森", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "還是說，那件事是錯的嗎？", "speakerName": "亞森", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "那麼……就只有反抗一途了。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "反抗……？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是啊。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那傢伙一直以來都在反抗唷。已經很長一段時間了。", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "MONA，為什麼你會在這？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為你看起來有點奇怪，吾輩有點在意就過來看看了。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是……被搶先一步了呢。真不愧是JOKER啊。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER他說的……『只有反抗一途』是什麼意思呢？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "其實那傢伙，有被人誣陷過。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "明明他什麼壞事都沒做，但卻被不講理的大人把未來給毀了……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER有著那種過去……？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。但是那傢伙貫徹了自己所相信的道路，拯救了吾輩與許多人……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "最終連世界都拯救了。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "JOKER他真是厲害啊……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為這樣，所以他比誰都還要清楚──", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "貫徹自己相信的道路有多困難……以及有多重要。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "自己相信的道路……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你好好問自己吧。過去做出的選擇，真的有錯嗎？", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你想貫徹的正義，究竟是什麼……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（我的正義，究竟是……？）", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "某天夜裡", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "可以打擾你一下嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。……已經做好覺悟了嗎？", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。我要去奪回大家的願望。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "即使會與埃米爾發生衝突，我也決定要那麼做了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是嗎……", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "謝謝你。多虧你，我已經想通了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他以前也會和我一起學習、有不懂的事情他也會教我……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "所以我也想過，究竟是從什麼時候開始，讓他走偏了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過，不管有什麼理由，現在埃米爾做的事情是不可原諒的。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "作為兄弟的話更是如此。我覺得自己非阻止他不可。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那就是你的決定了吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是的。我每次都感到非常迷惘。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不論是在多魯裂托斯山脈被輝龍強迫與埃米爾廝殺時，還有其他很多次都是。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，我每次都還是選擇了順從自己的正義。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這次我也必須這麼選擇。因為有你在，我才能重新審視自己，然後找出自己可以認同的答案。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……因為我們是夥伴啊。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你說得沒錯，真的是很感謝你。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……喂喂，你該不會忘記吾輩等人了吧？", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "大家……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只有你們兩個擅自關係變好……這有點不公平吧？", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我也想要幫上尤蒂爾的忙喔。", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們……什麼時候來的？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喵呵呵，這就是怪盜啊。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過是潛入房間這種事，太簡單了！……開玩笑的啦。", "speakerName": "PANTHER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在一旁偷聽抱歉啊。但是，大家都很擔心你喔。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒事嗎，尤蒂爾？", "speakerName": "SOPHIE", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。很抱歉讓你們擔心了……真的很謝謝你們。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們與我擁有著不同的價值觀，自從相遇了之後，我真的學習到很多。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那麼，就和最棒的夥伴們一起去完成最後的一件大事吧！首先是……", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "預告信，對吧。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，就這麼辦。把願望給收下！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "越來越有怪盜的樣子了，尤蒂爾。", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣就對了。", "speakerName": "MONA", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好，我們走吧。該完成我們的工作了！", "speakerName": "JOKER", "type": "conversation"}]}]